    "Extractive question answering in MLP.",
    "Extractive QA is a type of QA system that retrieves answers directly from a given passage of text rather than generating answers based on external knowledge or language understanding 40.",
    "It focuses on selecting and extracting the most relevant information from the passage to provide concise and accurate answers to specific questions.",
    "Extractive QA systems are commonly built using machine-learning techniques, including both supervised and unsupervised methods.",
    "Supervised learning approaches often require human-labelled training data, where questions and their corresponding answer spans in the passage are annotated."
  ],
